-- Hitachi Aims to Increase Overseas Procurement to 50% by Fiscal Year 2012
-- Jason Clenfield
-- 2010-06-15T02:03:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/hitachi-aims-to-increase-overseas-procurement-to-50-by-fiscal-year-2012.html

          
          
             Hitachi Ltd., a Japanese industrial
and electronics group that has lost money four years running,
plans to increase the portion of procurement from overseas to
half the total by the year ending March 2013.  
 The company currently sources an estimated 35 percent of
materials and other goods from outside Japan, it said in a
statement today in Tokyo.  
